Line: I mean... if you could tell me where I am... or why I'm here... that would be great.
What is the last thing you remember?
Yeah... And then I was here, and I found you.
Do you know who you are?
Forget it. I believe I saw something that belongs to you further behind me.
If I were you, I'd go look for it. Once you find it, press Z to collect it.
Then come back here. Hopefully, it will have jogged your memory.
